 AND HEAD BACK TO FENIA TO"}},{"data":{"text":"UPDATE THE MASTERCOPY, FOR WHAT FEW OTHER STARDRIFTERS MAY BE LEFT"}},{"data":{"text":". IF YOU'RE READING THIS, I SUCCEEDED, AND I HOPE THAT WHAT I'VE"}},{"data":{"text":"WRITTEN HAS BEEN VALUABLE IN SOME WAY TO YOU. ALSO THIS SYSTEM IS"}},{"data":{"text":"WEIRD, I'D STAY AND DO FURTHER RESEARCH BUT IT'S SPOOKING ME OUT."}},{"data":{"text":"SOME BRAVER EXPLORER CAN TAEK OVER FROM HERE. (TWOTWOS, 6012:247.2)"}},{"data":{"text":"OH RIGHT, THAT'S JUST BECAUSE NONE OF THEM WERE LABELLED. OKAY,"}},{"data":{"text":"I'M GETTING OUT OF HERE (TWOTWOS, 6012:247.3)"}}],"childrenPlanet":[{"id":"planet_2","data":{"name":"2","index":"12"},"fields":{"slug":"/planets/2"}},{"id":"planet_1","data":{"name":"1","index":"13"},"fields":{"slug":"/planets/1"}},{"id":"planet_THE ORANGE DEAL","data":{"name":"THE ORANGE DEAL","index":"17"},"fields":{"slug":"/planets/THE ORANGE DEAL"}},{"id":"planet_THE ORANGE MYSTERY","data":{"name":"THE ORANGE MYSTERY","index":"04"},"fields":{"slug":"/planets/THE ORANGE MYSTERY"}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/stars/ORANGE LIFE"}}}